Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:54.53,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Berdoa tak akan menghasilkan apapun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:56.90,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Aku tahu itu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.90,0:01:59.28,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Meski rasa takut kehilangan menghalangi kita,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:01.32,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}semua orang tetap menyongsong hari esok
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:03.83,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Tak melihat, tak peduli...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:08.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Mereka yang bahkan tak memberi kebebasan atau pun cinta,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:10.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}para malaikat dari langit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:13.42,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Firasatku berbicara, ya, aku suka takdir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:17.76,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Kupasrahkan diriku, kehendakku kepada sayap ini
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:22.68,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Tanpa lelah ku terus hidup di dunia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:26.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Jadilah pembela kebenaran meski hanya sandiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:30.52,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Aku ingin kebahagiaan tertinggi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:38.28,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Hanya itu saja
